## A/B Testing and Canary Deployment

### Traffic Splitting

| Deployment Phase | Control Traffic | Treatment Traffic | Duration |
|-----------------|-----------------|-------------------|----------|
| Shadow mode | 100% | 0% (shadow) | 1-2 weeks |
| Canary | 95% | 5% | 1 week |
| Ramp | 50% | 50% | 1 week |
| Full rollout | 0% | 100% | Permanent |

### Shadow Mode

Shadow mode runs the new model alongside the old model without affecting users:

```python
async def predict_with_shadow(features: dict) -> float:
    primary_result = primary_model.predict(features)

    # Shadow prediction -- fire and forget
    asyncio.create_task(shadow_predict(features, primary_result))

    return primary_result

async def shadow_predict(features: dict, primary_result: float):
    shadow_result = shadow_model.predict(features)
    metrics.log_shadow_comparison(primary_result, shadow_result)
```

