## Health Checks

### Liveness Check

```python
@app.get("/health/live")
async def liveness():
    return {"status": "ok"}
```

### Readiness Check

```python
@app.get("/health/ready")
async def readiness():
    if model is None:
        raise HTTPException(503, "Model not loaded")
    if not feature_store.is_healthy():
        raise HTTPException(503, "Feature store unavailable")
    return {"status": "ready", "model_version": MODEL_VERSION}
```

